VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (System\.out\.print|System\.err\.print|System\.out\.println|System\.err\.println|log\.(debug|trace))
WHEN EXPR MISSING:release|production
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of debugging and logging statements (System.out.print, System.err.print, System.out.println, System.err.println, log.debug, log.trace), which may expose sensitive backend information if used in the production environment.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Debugging and Logging Statements.
